    "description_long": "This is a compact, rectangular Emerson radio receiver with a predominantly white plastic body and a blue-tinted translucent cassette compartment on the front. The left side features a perforated speaker grille, while the right side displays the Emerson logo and product labeling. A telescopic metal antenna extends from the top, and a row of control buttons and dials is visible along the upper surface. The back panel includes ventilation slits, a battery compartment, and a product information label. The overall design is utilitarian, with rounded edges and a handle integrated into the top for portability.",
